nodes.text: The Clone Wars: Hunting the Hunters (Part I)

The Clone Wars: Hunting the Hunters (Part I) is a short webcomic that was released between Seasons One and Two of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series. The game Gunship Over Florrum was also posted on StarWars.com as a tie-in to the comic. Both feature a Republic mission to Florrum. An extra page of the comic was presented for being able to shoot down Shahan Alama's saucer craft.
